    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >和奋力拼搏的史莱姆们一起，展开热闹混战的夺旗对战！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不断增加史莱姆的数量，收集场地上的旗子，谁收集得更多，谁就获胜！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >史莱姆们会按照你的指令奔跑、搬运、战斗， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使被压扁，也会努力不懈、拼命向前。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但别担心，他们会马上复活，再次为你奋战！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和朋友、家人一起，享受热闹欢乐的混战对决吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不论是本地分屏游玩，还是线上对战，都能轻松畅玩！ <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084910/extras/24dcaf8d22015f1d221ca8a612b0fb6c.poster.avif?t=1760666304\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084910/extras/24dcaf8d22015f1d221ca8a612b0fb6c.webm?t=1760666304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084910/extras/24dcaf8d22015f1d221ca8a612b0fb6c.mp4?t=1760666304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >以“心理博弈”拉开胜负差距，简单却极富深度的策略对决！ </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作虽简单，真正掌握胜负关键的，是“出其不意的战术布局”和“快速的判断能力”。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你要把史莱姆派往哪里？守住旗子？夺旗反攻？还是搭墙阻敌？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在有限的指令中展开的“心理博弈”，才是决定胜负的关键！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完全没有复杂操作。但别被可爱的外表欺骗了！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款硬核玩家也非常适合的对战游戏！ <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084910/extras/c4735f9acb4d99bebd17e25d859d20bd.poster.avif?t=1760666304\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084910/extras/c4735f9acb4d99bebd17e25d859d20bd.webm?t=1760666304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084910/extras/c4735f9acb4d99bebd17e25d859d20bd.mp4?t=1760666304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Jelly Troops》的特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人人都能轻松上手的简单即时战略（RTS）游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隐秘潜行的“偷旗”玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡通渲染风格的可爱图像与动画演出</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持与全球玩家进行随机匹配对战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >节奏明快的游戏体验，让人忍不住一局接一局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和朋友一起的私人房间对战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只需一份游戏即可本地分屏双人对战（本地分屏对战需要控制器）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使一个人也能挑战的单人模式</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084910/extras/a14fd4281cca7b4e32eeb94efb0e0e46.poster.avif?t=1760666304\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084910/extras/a14fd4281cca7b4e32eeb94efb0e0e46.webm?t=1760666304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084910/extras/a14fd4281cca7b4e32eeb94efb0e0e46.mp4?t=1760666304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
